// [Security Justification] 
// The content being processed here is obtained exclusively from the Weffocus server via a BufferedInputStream (bos). 
// It is written using bos.write(b), where 'b' represents the byte array fetched directly from the trusted server. 
// This content is not sourced from user input and there is no opportunity for user intervention or manipulation. 
// Therefore, there is no risk of injection of scripts or other malicious code through this mechanism.